



Dining philosopher simulates a situation where multiple threads are completing for dependent resources to complete a task
and since each thread is waiting for other thread to release the resource they are forever stuck.

Setup -

There are five philosopher who needs two chopstick to eat spaghatti. A philosopher can eat only when he has both the chopstick.
A philosopher can be in two modes either THINKING or EATING.

1. As step 1 each philosopher picks up one chopstick each
2. And waits for the second chopstick to start eating.